 GENERAL:

   ESC                  exit BeatDrop / menus
   ALT + ENTER          toggle fullscreen (or double-click)
   ALT + S              toggle multiple monitor stretch
   CTRL + Z             enable/disable spout output
   CTRL + D             toggle output/input audio device
   CTRL + T             instantly reset time variable
   SHIFT + UP           increase window opacity
   SHIFT + DOWN         decrease window opacity
   Q                    automatic/manual beat sensitivity mode
   UP                   increase beat sensetivity (only manual mode)
   DOWN                 decrease beat sensetivity (only manual mode)

 PRESETS:

   SPACE / H            soft / hard cut to next preset
   BACKSPACE            go back to previous preset
   ` / ~                [un]lock current preset
   R                    toggle random/sequential preset order 
   L                    load specific preset
   M                    show/hide preset-editing menu
   S                    save new preset
   A                    do random mini-mash-up
   D                    toggle warp & comp shader locks
   !                    randomize warp shader
   @                    randomize comp shader

 INFO:

   F1                   show/hide help
   F4                   show/hide preset info
   F5                   show/hide fps
   F6                   show/hide rating
   F8                   show/hide song title
   
 HOTKEYS:

   F2                   toggle borderless window (untoggleable while on fullscreen or stretch mode)
   F3                   toggle fps to 30/60/90/120/144/240/360/Unlimited
   F7                   always on top
   F11                  hardcut mode: normal/based of music
   F12                  transparency mode (removes the black background)
   N                    show/hide per-frame monitor
   P                    force transition blend pattern

 PLAYBACK:

   Z                    previous track
   X                    play/pause track
   C                    stop track
   V                    next track
   LEFT ARROW           rewind track (seek -5 seconds)
   RIGHT ARROW          fast forward track (seek +5 seconds)

 CUSTOM SPRITES/MESSAGES:

   K                    enter sprite mode
   SHIFT + K            enter sprite kill mode
   Y                    enter custom message mode
   00-99                invoke sprites/messages (clears some sprites while you introduced some digits - sprite kill mode)
   *                    clears the number of digits that you introduced
   DEL                  clear latest sprite from the slot/message
   SHIFT + DEL          clear oldest sprite from the slot/message
   SHIFT + CTRL + DEL   clear all the sprites/messages
   CTRL + K             kills all the sprites
   CTRL + T             kills custom messages/song titles

